ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[The number of positive laboratory confirmations among the Diamond Princess quarantined (passengers and crew) continues to grow. One suspects there are a multitude of reasons behind this -- possible fomite contamination of surfaces, the air duct systems aboard the boat, crew living in dormitory-like conditions with multiple people to a room, individuals not following correct use of PPE (personal protective equipment) to name a few.

It is noteworthy that 14 of the 338 evacuees transferred back to the USA were found to be infected with the coronavirus (the SARS-CoV-2 virus is responsible for the disease COVID-19) (figures on evacuees came from a NY Times/Reuters article https://www.nytimes.com/reuters/2020/02/17/world/asia/17reuters-china-health-japan-cruiseship.html. - Mod.MPP]

